{"type":"message","id":"fb3765a6","parentId":"909e82fd","timestamp":"2026-02-28T20:31:56.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，Skills 已经改进。现在让我创建一个综合的系统健康自动修复脚本，并更新进化历史。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"### C. 生成修复脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0689098f92f64bbdb3f6a823","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/auto-health-recovery.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# 系统健康自动恢复脚本\n# 用途：当健康评分 < 6.0 时自动执行恢复操作\n# 创建：2026-03-01 Round 259\n# 关联 Pattern：PAT-048, PAT-049, PAT-050, PAT-051\n\nset -e\n\n# 颜色输出\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/health-recovery-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).log\"\n\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $1\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nlog \"🚀 开始系统健康自动恢复...\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 1: 检查系统状态\n# ============================================\nlog \"📊 Phase 1: 检查系统状态...\"\n\n# 检查 Gateway 内存\nGATEWAY_MEM=$(ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $6}')\nif [ -n \"$GATEWAY_MEM\" ]; then\n    GATEWAY_MB=$((GATEWAY_MEM / 1024))\n    log \"Gateway 内存使用: ${GATEWAY_MB} MB\"\n    \n    if [ $GATEWAY_MB -gt 1200 ]; then\n        log \"${RED}⚠️ Gateway 内存过高 (${GATEWAY_MB} MB)，执行重启...${NC}\"\n        \"$WORKSPACE/evolver/fixes/gateway-emergency-restart.sh\"\n        sleep 10\n    fi\nfi\n\n# 检查系统可用内存\nAVAILABLE_MEM=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\nlog \"系统可用内存: ${AVAILABLE_MEM} MB\"\n\nif [ $AVAILABLE_MEM -lt 500 ]; then\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ 可用内存不足，执行清理...${NC}\"\n    \"$WORKSPACE/evolver/fixes/emergency-memory-free.sh\"\nfi\n\n# 检查磁盘空间\nDISK_USAGE=$(df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $5}' | sed 's/%//')\nlog \"磁盘使用率: ${DISK_USAGE}%\"\n\nif [ $DISK_USAGE -gt 80 ]; then\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ 磁盘空间紧张，执行清理...${NC}\"\n    \"$WORKSPACE/evolver/fixes/disk-cleanup.sh\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 2: API 健康检查\n# ============================================\nlog \"🔍 Phase 2: API 健康检查...\"\n\n# 检查最近 1 小时的 429 错误\nRECENT_429=$(find \"$WORKSPACE\" -name \"*.txt\" -path \"*/agent-transcripts/*\" -mmin -60 2>/dev/null | \\\n    xargs grep -l \"429\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n\nif [ $RECENT_429 -gt 10 ]; then\n    log \"${RED}🚨 检测到大量 429 错误 (${RECENT_429} 个文件)，API 可能余额不足${NC}\"\n    log \"建议操作：\"\n    log \"1. 检查智谱 AI 账户余额\"\n    log \"2. 运行 api-balance-monitor.sh\"\n    log \"3. 考虑暂停非关键 cron 任务\"\n    \n    # 自动降低频率（可选）\n    # log \"正在降低 cron 任务频率...\"\n    # crontab -l | sed 's|*/15|*/30|g' | crontab -\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 3: 子代理清理\n# ============================================\nlog \"🤖 Phase 3: 子代理清理...\"\n\n# 检查是否有僵尸子代理进程\nZOMBIE_COUNT=$(ps aux | grep \"sessions_spawn\" | grep -v grep | wc -l)\nif [ $ZOMBIE_COUNT -gt 5 ]; then\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ 检测到 ${ZOMBIE_COUNT} 个子代理进程，建议检查${NC}\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 4: 网络检查\n# ============================================\nlog \"🌐 Phase 4: 网络检查...\"\n\n# 检查 Gateway 连接\nGATEWAY_STATUS=$(systemctl is-active openclaw-gateway 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")\nlog \"Gateway 状态: ${GATEWAY_STATUS}\"\n\nif [ \"$GATEWAY_STATUS\" != \"active\" ]; then\n    log \"${RED}⚠️ Gateway 未运行，尝试启动...${NC}\"\n    systemctl start openclaw-gateway 2>/dev/null || openclaw gateway start\n    sleep 5\nfi\n\n# 检查网络连通性\nif ! ping -c 1 -W 5 8.8.8.8 > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ 网络连接异常${NC}\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 5: 生成健康报告\n# ============================================\nlog \"📝 Phase 5: 生成健康报告...\"\n\nREPORT_FILE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/health-status-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).md\"\n\ncat > \"$REPORT_FILE\" << EOF\n# 系统健康状态报告\n\n**生成时间**: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n**执行脚本**: auto-health-recovery.sh\n\n## 系统指标\n\n| 指标 | 当前值 | 状态 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| Gateway 内存 | ${GATEWAY_MB:-N/A} MB | $([ ${GATEWAY_MB:-0} -lt 1200 ] && echo \"✅ 正常\" || echo \"⚠️ 偏高\") |\n| 可用内存 | ${AVAILABLE_MEM} MB | $([ $AVAILABLE_MEM -gt 500 ] && echo \"✅ 充足\" || echo \"⚠️ 紧张\") |\n| 磁盘使用 | ${DISK_USAGE}% | $([ $DISK_USAGE -lt 80 ] && echo \"✅ 正常\" || echo \"⚠️ 偏高\") |\n| Gateway 状态 | ${GATEWAY_STATUS} | $([ \"$GATEWAY_STATUS\" = \"active\" ] && echo \"✅ 运行中\" || echo \"⚠️ 异常\") |\n| 最近 429 错误 | ${RECENT_429} 个文件 | $([ $RECENT_429 -lt 10 ] && echo \"✅ 正常\" || echo \"🚨 严重\") |\n\n## 执行的恢复操作\n\n$(cat \"$LOG_FILE\" | grep -E \"^(执行|重启|清理)\" || echo \"无\")\n\n## 建议\n\n$(if [ $RECENT_429 -gt 10 ]; then\n    echo \"- 🚨 **立即检查 API 余额**\"\n    echo \"- 考虑暂停非关键任务\"\nfi)\n$(if [ ${GATEWAY_MB:-0} -gt 1200 ]; then\n    echo \"- ⚠️ 监控 Gateway 内存泄漏\"\nfi)\n$(if [ $AVAILABLE_MEM -lt 500 ]; then\n    echo \"- ⚠️ 系统内存不足，考虑扩容\"\nfi)\n\n## 相关 Patterns\n\n- PAT-048: 429 速率限制\n- PAT-049: Gateway 超时\n- PAT-050: Unknown subagent\n- PAT-051: Network error\n\n---\n*报告由 auto-health-recovery.sh 自动生成*\nEOF\n\nlog \"✅ 健康报告已生成: $REPORT_FILE\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 6: 总结\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"🎉 系统健康恢复完成\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"详细日志: $LOG_FILE\"\nlog \"健康报告: $REPORT_FILE\"\nlog \"\"\n\n# 返回健康评分（简化版）\nHEALTH_SCORE=10\n[ $RECENT_429 -gt 10 ] && HEALTH_SCORE=$((HEALTH_SCORE - 3))\n[ ${GATEWAY_MB:-0} -gt 1200 ] && HEALTH_SCORE=$((HEALTH_SCORE - 2))\n[ $AVAILABLE_MEM -lt 500 ] && HEALTH_SCORE=$((HEALTH_SCORE - 2))\n[ $DISK_USAGE -gt 80 ] && HEALTH_SCORE=$((HEALTH_SCORE - 1))\n\nlog \"预估健康评分: ${HEALTH_SCORE}/10\"\n\nif [ $HEALTH_SCORE -lt 6 ]; then\n    log \"${RED}⚠️ 系统健康评分较低，建议人工检查${NC}\"\n    exit 1\nelse\n    log \"${GREEN}✅ 系统状态良好${NC}\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dfb160f0bf3a4a568563bbd1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/auto-health-recovery.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":700,"output":2012,"cacheRead":33984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36696,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772310661717}}
