\n\n## 🚨 紧急行动建议\n\n### 立即执行（今天上午 8:00）\n\n1. **检查 API 余额** (P0 - 最紧急)\n   ```bash\n   /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/api-balance-monitor.sh\n   ```\n   **原因**: 429 错误激增 157%，最可能是余额不足\n\n2. **运行健康恢复脚本** (P0)\n   ```bash\n   /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/auto-health-recovery.sh\n   ```\n   **预期**: 自动检测并修复系统问题\n\n3. **配置自动健康检查** (P0)\n   ```bash\n   # 添加到 crontab（每 4 小时）\n   0 */4 * * * /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/auto-health-recovery.sh\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 系统状态\n\n- **健康评分**: 3.5/10 (🔴 严重)\n- **Pattern 解决率**: 37/53 (70%)\n- **Skills 数量**: 38 个\n- **修复脚本**: 22 个\n- **趋势**: 需要立即执行 P0 修复\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 任务完成\n\n本轮自进化任务已完成所有要求的改进措施：\n- ✅ A. 创建新 Skill - 不适用（已有相关 Skills）\n- ✅ B. 改进现有 Skill - 2 个 Skills 改进\n- ✅ C. 生成修复脚本 - 1 个自动化脚本\n- ✅ D. 更新进化历史 - Pattern 解决率提升\n\n**详细报告**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evolution-2026-03-01-0430.md`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1327,"output":1168,"cacheRead":41280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43775,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772310843833}}
