252 | Round 254 | 3→12 | 🔴高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1200.md |\n| PAT-044 | [任务] Task aborted → 任务被迫中止 | 任务 | Round 252 | Round 254 | 2→26 | 🔴高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1200.md |\n| PAT-045 | [代理] Unknown subagent target → 子代理管理失败 | 代理 | Round 252 | Round 254 | 2→26 | 🔴高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1200.md |\n| PAT-046 | [操作] Edit 匹配失败 → 文件编辑重试 | 操作 | Round 252 | Round 258 | 11→28 | 🔧有方案 | skills/smart-file-edit/SKILL.md |\n| PAT-047 | [文件] ENOENT 路径错误 → 文件读取失败 | 文件 | Round 252 | Round 254 | 1→2 | 🟢低风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-02-28-1200.md |\n| PAT-048 | [API] 429 速率限制激增 → 196 次失败 | API | Round 254 | Round 259 | 76→178 | 🟡改善中 | skills/peak-hours-monitoring/SKILL.md |\n| PAT-049 | [连接] Gateway 超时激增 → 22 次通信中断 | 连接 | Round 254 | Round 259 | 12→11 | ✅已改善 | memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0800.md |\n| PAT-050 | [代理] Unknown subagent 激增 → 56 次管理失败 | 代理 | Round 254 | Round 258 | 26→56 | 🔧有方案 | skills/subagent-lifecycle-manager/SKILL.md |\n| PAT-051 | [网络] Network error 激增 → 42 次 API 调用失败 | 网络 | Round 254 | Round 259 | 20→27 | 🔧有方案 | skills/network-error-monitor/SKILL.md |\n| PAT-052 | [任务] Task aborted 激增 → 48 次任务中断 | 任务 | Round 254 | Round 257 | 26→48 | 🔴高风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0000.md |\n| PAT-053 | [文件] EISDIR 错误 → 尝试读取目录 | 文件 | Round 254 | Round 257 | 1 | 🟢低风险 | memory/log-analysis-2026-03-01-0000.md |\n\n[170 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772339422957}}
{"type":"message","id":"9fb628f3","parentId":"ecea7891","timestamp":"2026-03-01T04:30:42.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，分析完最新的日志报告，我发现：\n\n**系统状态**:\n- 健康评分: 5.5/10（从 5.8 略降至 5.5，-0.3）\n- 429 错误: 115 次（从 178 降至 115，-35%，持续改善）\n- Gateway 超时: 16 次（从 11 增至 16，+5）\n- Network Error: 48 次（新增监控）\n- ENOENT 错误: 37 次（从 18 增至 37，+106%）\n- 子代理错误: 28 次（从 20 增至 28，+8）\n- 内存使用: 2179 MB（从 2367 降至 2179，-188 MB，改善）\n\n**关键发现**:\n1. 🟢 429 错误持续大幅改善（从 221 → 178 → 115，总共 -48%）\n2. 🟢 内存使用改善（可用内存 +194 MB）\n3. 🟡 健康评分略降（5.8 → 5.5，-0.3）\n4. 🟡 Network Error 新增（48 次）\n5. 🔴 ENOENT 错误增加（从 18 增至 37，+106%）\n\n**需要改进的地方**:\n1. Network Error 需要监控和恢复机制（已有 network-error-monitor Skill）\n2. ENOENT 错误增加，需要文件存在性检查\n\n\n3. Gateway 和子代理错误需要持续监控，同时 SWE-Agent-Node 迭代成功率为 63.2%。\n\n接下来我需要创建 Skill 或改进现有 Skill 来解决 ENOENT 错误问题，以及优化文件操作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Phase 2: 深度分析（续）"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e16ed23583d648a1815e7213","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lh /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b10ca205e21b4870abea4d1f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lh /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/*.sh 2>/dev/null | wc -l"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f32f501e23145ddad6ee27c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"free -m && echo \"---\" && ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print \"Gateway Memory: \"$6/1024\" MB\"}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":6537,"output":524,"cacheRead":67520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74581,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772339422961}}
