{"type":"message","id":"23262f41","parentId":"1521da2d","timestamp":"2026-03-01T08:31:51.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从日志分析报告可以看到：\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. 健康评分从 5.5 降至 5.0 (-0.5)\n2. 429 错误反弹：从 115 增至 156 (+36%)\n3. Network Error 增加：从 48 增至 74 (+54%)\n4. ENOENT 错误大幅增加：从 37 增至 64 (+73%)\n5. 任务中断翻倍：从 19 增至 38 (+100%)\n6. Gateway 内存增加：从 1022 MB 增至 1135 MB (+113 MB)\n\n**根本原因**：\n- 多个 cron 任务在相近时间触发\n- API 请求频率再次上升\n- 可能触发了新的 API 配额周期\n\n**改进建议**：\n1. 调整 Cron 任务调度 - 错开多个 cron 任务的执行时间\n2. 实施 API 请求队列\n3. 监控 Gateway 内存\n\n我需要执行主动改进。根据日志分析，我应该：\n\n1. **C. 生成修复脚本** - 创建一个 cron 任务调度优化脚本，自动错开任务执行时间\n2. **B. 改进现有 Skill** - 改进相关 Skills\n3. **D. 更新进化历史** - 记录本轮发现\n\n让我开始执行改进...","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Phase 3: 主动改进\n\n基于分析，系统出现反弹，需要立即执行改进：\n\n### C. 生成修复脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5d2b7a1faf3d41c7a0095e4d","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Cron 任务自动错峰调度脚本\n# 用途：自动调整 cron 任务执行时间，避免 API 竞争和 429 错误\n# 创建：2026-03-01 Round 262\n# 关联 Pattern：PAT-048, PAT-026, PAT-018\n\nset -e\n\n# 颜色输出\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"\nBACKUP_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/cron-backups\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/cron-stagger-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).log\"\n\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $1\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nlog \"🚀 开始 Cron 任务自动错峰调度...\"\n\n# 创建备份目录\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_DIR\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 1: 备份当前 crontab\n# ============================================\nlog \"📦 Phase 1: 备份当前 crontab...\"\n\nBACKUP_FILE=\"$BACKUP_DIR/crontab.$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).bak\"\ncrontab -l > \"$BACKUP_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"# Empty crontab\" > \"$BACKUP_FILE\"\n\nlog \"✅ 备份已保存: $BACKUP_FILE\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 2: 分析当前任务\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"📊 Phase 2: 分析当前任务...\"\n\nCURRENT_CRON=$(crontab -l 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\nif [ -z \"$CURRENT_CRON\" ] || [ \"$CURRENT_CRON\" = \"# Empty crontab\" ]; then\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ 当前没有 crontab 任务${NC}\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\n# 统计任务数量\nTOTAL_TASKS=$(echo \"$CURRENT_CRON\" | grep -v \"^#\" | grep -v \"^$\" | wc -l)\nlog \"当前任务总数: ${TOTAL_TASKS}\"\n\n# 分析任务分布（按小时）\nlog \"\"\nlog \"当前任务分布（按小时）:\"\ndeclare -A HOUR_COUNT\nwhile IFS= read -r line; do\n    if [[ ! \"$line\" =~ ^# ]] && [[ -n \"$line\" ]]; then\n        hour=$(echo \"$line\" | awk '{print $2}')\n        if [[ \"$hour\" =~ ^[0-9]+$ ]]; then\n            HOUR_COUNT[$hour]=$((${HOUR_COUNT[$hour]:-0} + 1))\n        fi\n    fi\ndone <<< \"$CURRENT_CRON\"\n\nfor hour in $(echo \"${!HOUR_COUNT[@]}\" | tr ' ' '\\n' | sort -n); do\n    count=${HOUR_COUNT[$hour]}\n    log \"  $(printf '%02d' $hour):00 - $count 个任务\"\ndone\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 3: 识别冲突任务\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"🔍 Phase 3: 识别冲突任务...\"\n\n# 定义高峰期（基于 PAT-018, PAT-024, PAT-023）\nHIGH_PEAK_HOURS=\"07 08 09 10 15 16\"\nMEDIUM_PEAK_HOURS=\"11 12 13 14 17\"\nLOW_PEAK_HOURS=\"00 01 02 03 04 05 06 18 19 20 21 22 23\"\n\n# 统计高峰期任务\nHIGH_PEAK_COUNT=0\nfor hour in $HIGH_PEAK_HOURS; do\n    HIGH_PEAK_COUNT=$((HIGH_PEAK_COUNT + ${HOUR_COUNT[$hour]:-0}))\ndone\n\nlog \"高峰期任务数: ${HIGH_PEAK_COUNT} / ${TOTAL_TASKS}\"\n\nif [ $HIGH_PEAK_COUNT -gt 3 ]; then\n    log \"${RED}⚠️ 高峰期任务过多 (${HIGH_PEAK_COUNT} 个)，需要错峰调度${NC}\"\n    NEED_STAGGER=1\nelse\n    log \"${GREEN}✅ 高峰期任务分布合理${NC}\"\n    NEED_STAGGER=0\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 4: 生成错峰调度方案\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"💡 Phase 4: 生成错峰调度方案...\"\n\nSTAGGERED_CRON=\"\"\nTASK_INDEX=0\n\nwhile IFS= read -r line; do\n    if [[ \"$line\" =~ ^# ]] || [[ -z \"$line\" ]]; then\n        # 保留注释和空行\n        STAGGERED_CRON=\"${STAGGERED_CRON}${line}\"$'\\n'\n        continue\n    fi\n    \n    # 解析 cron 表达式\n    minute=$(echo \"$line\" | awk '{print $1}')\n    hour=$(echo \"$line\" | awk '{print $2}')\n    day=$(echo \"$line\" | awk '{print $3}')\n    month=$(echo \"$line\" | awk '{print $4}')\n    weekday=$(echo \"$line\" | awk '{print $5}')\n    command=$(echo \"$line\" | cut -d' ' -f6-)\n    \n    # 检查是否在高峰期\n    NEED_MOVE=0\n    NEW_HOUR=$hour\n    \n    if echo \"$HIGH_PEAK_HOURS\" | grep -qw \"$hour\"; then\n        NEED_MOVE=1\n        # 根据任务索引选择低峰期时间\n        case $TASK_INDEX in\n            0) NEW_HOUR=\"02\" ;;  # 移到凌晨 2 点\n            1) NEW_HOUR=\"03\" ;;  # 移到凌晨 3 点\n            2) NEW_HOUR=\"04\" ;;  # 移到凌晨 4 点\n            3) NEW_HOUR=\"05\" ;;  # 移到凌晨 5 点\n            4) NEW_HOUR=\"18\" ;;  # 移到晚上 6 点\n            5) NEW_HOUR=\"19\" ;;  # 移到晚上 7 点\n            6) NEW_HOUR=\"20\" ;;  # 移到晚上 8 点\n            7) NEW_HOUR=\"21\" ;;  # 移到晚上 9 点\n            8) NEW_HOUR=\"22\" ;;  # 移到晚上 10 点\n            9) NEW_HOUR=\"23\" ;;  # 移到晚上 11 点\n            *) NEW_HOUR=\"00\" ;;  # 移到凌晨 0 点\n        esac\n        \n        log \"  调整任务 $TASK_INDEX: ${hour}:$(printf '%02d' $minute) → ${NEW_HOUR}:$(printf '%02d' $minute)\"\n    fi\n    \n    # 生成新的 cron 行\n    if [ $NEED_MOVE -eq 1 ]; then\n        NEW_LINE=\"$minute $NEW_HOUR $day $month $weekday $command\"\n    else\n        NEW_LINE=\"$line\"\n    fi\n    \n    STAGGERED_CRON=\"${STAGGERED_CRON}${NEW_LINE}\"$'\\n'\n    TASK_INDEX=$((TASK_INDEX + 1))\ndone <<< \"$CURRENT_CRON\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 5: 应用错峰调度（需要确认）\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"📊 错峰调度分析完成\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"\"\n\nif [ $NEED_STAGGER -eq 1 ]; then\n    log \"原 crontab:\"\n    echo \"$CURRENT_CRON\" | grep -v \"^#\" | grep -v \"^$\" | head -10\n    \n    log \"\"\n    log \"调整后 crontab:\"\n    echo \"$STAGGERED_CRON\" | grep -v \"^#\" | grep -v \"^$\" | head -10\n    \n    log \"\"\n    log \"备份文件: $BACKUP_FILE\"\n    log \"日志文件: $LOG_FILE\"\n    log \"\"\n    \n    # 检查是否有 --apply 参数\n    if [ \"$1\" = \"--apply\" ]; then\n        log \"${YELLOW}应用错峰调度...${NC}\"\n        echo \"$STAGGERED_CRON\" | crontab -\n        log \"${GREEN}✅ 错峰调度已应用${NC}\"\n        \n        # 重启 cron 服务\n        systemctl restart cron 2>/dev/null || service cron restart 2>/dev/null || true\n        log \"✅ Cron 服务已重启\"\n    else\n        log \"${YELLOW}预览模式 - 未应用更改${NC}\"\n        log \"要应用更改，请运行:\"\n        log \"  $0 --apply\"\n        log \"\"\n        log \"或手动编辑 crontab:\"\n        log \"  crontab -e\"\n    fi\nelse\n    log \"${GREEN}✅ 无需错峰调度，当前任务分布合理${NC}\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 6: 生成报告\n# ============================================\nREPORT_FILE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/cron-stagger-report-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).md\"\n\ncat > \"$REPORT_FILE\" << EOF\n# Cron 任务错峰调度报告\n\n**生成时间**: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n\n## 当前状态\n\n- 总任务数: ${TOTAL_TASKS}\n- 高峰期任务数: ${HIGH_PEAK_COUNT}\n- 需要错峰调度: $([ $NEED_STAGGER -eq 1 ] && echo \"是\" || echo \"否\")\n\n## 任务分布\n\n### 按小时统计\n\nEOF\n\nfor hour in $(seq 0 23); do\n    count=${HOUR_COUNT[$hour]:-0}\n    if [ $count -gt 0 ]; then\n        echo \"- $(printf '%02d' $hour):00 - $count 个任务\" >> \"$REPORT_FILE\"\n    fi\ndone\n\ncat >> \"$REPORT_FILE\" << EOF\n\n## 高峰期定义\n\n- 🔴 极高: 10:00（历史最高峰）\n- 🔴 高: 07:00-09:00, 15:00-16:00\n- 🟡 中: 11:00-14:00, 17:00\n- 🟢 低: 00:00-06:00, 18:00-23:00\n\n## 调整建议\n\n$([ $NEED_STAGGER -eq 1 ] && echo \"建议将高峰期任务移动到低峰期执行\" || echo \"当前任务分布合理，无需调整\")\n\n## 文件\n\n- 备份: $BACKUP_FILE\n- 日志: $LOG_FILE\n\n---\n*报告由 cron-stagger.sh 自动生成*\nEOF\n\nlog \"\"\nlog \"📄 报告已生成: $REPORT_FILE\"\n\nexit 0\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/cron-stagger.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9c7f576ae7a343acb0786889","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/cron-stagger.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3376,"output":2703,"cacheRead":87616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93695,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772353825072}}
