{"type":"message","id":"7477218f","parentId":"6dc2bf4b","timestamp":"2026-03-01T08:32:16.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经创建了一个 cron 任务错峰调度脚本。现在我需要：\n\n1. 改进现有 Skill - 特别是 network-error-monitor 和 file-existence-checker\n2. 更新进化历史\n\n让我继续...","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"### B. 改进现有 Skill"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_358809b4c736414496d21aed","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/network-error-monitor/SKILL.md","limit":50}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c15112b621284c1d8efd8da0","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/network-error-monitor/SKILL.md","oldText":"## 核心问题\n\n**PAT-051**: Network Error\n- 出现次数: 27+ 次（Round 259 新增监控）\n- 根本原因:\n  1. 网络不稳定\n  2. API 服务端问题\n  3. Gateway 连接超时\n  4. DNS 解析失败","newText":"## 核心问题\n\n**PAT-051**: Network Error\n- 出现次数: 74 次（Round 261，从 48 增至 74，+54%）\n- 根本原因:\n  1. 网络不稳定\n  2. API 服务端问题\n  3. Gateway 连接超时\n  4. DNS 解析失败\n  5. **新问题（2026-03-01 16:00）**: 多个 cron 任务并发触发 API 竞争"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6bfa43d598f64590919e3f6e","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/network-error-monitor/SKILL.md","oldText":"## 监控指标\n\n| 指标 | 正常值 | 警告值 | 严重值 |\n|------|--------|--------|--------|\n| 外网连通性 | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| DNS 解析 | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| Gateway 状态 | active | inactive | unknown |\n| network_error (1h) | <5 | 5-10 | >10 |\n| Gateway 超时 (1h) | <3 | 3-10 | >10 |","newText":"## 监控指标\n\n| 指标 | 正常值 | 警告值 | 严重值 |\n|------|--------|--------|--------|\n| 外网连通性 | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| DNS 解析 | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| Gateway 状态 | active | inactive | unknown |\n| network_error (1h) | <5 | 5-10 | >10 |\n| Gateway 超时 (1h) | <3 | 3-10 | >10 |\n\n## 🚨 紧急应对措施（2026-03-01 更新）\n\n当 Network Error > 50 次/6h 时：\n1. **立即执行 cron-stagger.sh**\n   ```bash\n   /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/cron-stagger.sh --apply\n   ```\n2. **检查 Gateway 状态**\n   ```bash\n   systemctl status openclaw-gateway\n   ```\n3. **监控 API 使用情况**\n   - 检查智谱 AI 账户配额\n   - 考虑降低请求频率"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2786,"output":705,"cacheRead":90944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94435,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772353911473}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1c6c5d6","parentId":"7477218f","timestamp":"2026-03-01T08:32:16.578Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_358809b4c736414496d21aed","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: network-error-monitor\ndescription: 网络错误监控与自动恢复。适用于：(1) 遇到 network_error 错误、(2) API 调用失败、(3) 远程通信中断、(4) 需要自动重试和恢复网络请求。\n---\n\n# Network Error Monitor - 网络错误监控与自动恢复\n\n监控网络错误并自动执行恢复操作，提高系统网络稳定性。\n\n## 核心问题\n\n**PAT-051**: Network Error\n- 出现次数: 27+ 次（Round 259 新增监控）\n- 根本原因:\n  1. 网络不稳定\n  2. API 服务端问题\n  3. Gateway 连接超时\n  4. DNS 解析失败\n\n## 监控维度\n\n### 1. 网络连通性\n\n```bash\n# 检查外网连通性\nping -c 1 -W 5 8.8.8.8\n\n# 检查 DNS 解析\nnslookup api.openai.com\n\n# 检查 Gateway 状态\nsystemctl is-active openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n### 2. API 健康检查\n\n```bash\n# 检查最近 1 小时的 network_error\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace -name \"*.txt\" -path \"*/agent-transcripts/*\" -mmin -60 | \\\n    xargs grep -l \"network_error\" | wc -l\n```\n\n### 3. Gateway 连接\n\n```bash\n# 检查 Gateway 内存\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | awk '{print $6}'\n\n# 检查 Gateway 超时\ngrep -r \"Gateway timeout\" /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/*.md | wc -l\n\n[231 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772353936574}}
