{"type":"message","id":"f846183f","parentId":"5b49e3a6","timestamp":"2026-03-01T12:31:18.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"非常严重的情况！Gateway 内存从 1135 MB 增加到 1450 MB，而且日志显示 20:00 时已经达到 1602 MB。系统可用内存只有 761 MB（日志显示 649 MB），这是非常危险的。\n\n健康评分从 5.0 降至 3.8，这是严重下降。\n\n需要立即采取行动：\n1. 重启 Gateway 服务\n2. 创建 Gateway 内存监控脚本\n3. 更新进化历史\n\n这是紧急情况，必须立即处理。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🚨 紧急情况检测\n\n**Gateway 内存泄漏严重**：\n- 当前：1450 MB\n- 4小时前：1135 MB\n- 增长：+315 MB (+28%)\n- 健康评分：3.8/10（严重下降）\n\n## Phase 3: 主动改进（紧急）\n\n### C. 生成紧急修复脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8bbc952da78d4d8187ea5ced","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Gateway 内存泄漏紧急修复脚本\n# 用途：检测并修复 Gateway 内存泄漏问题\n# 创建：2026-03-01 Round 263\n# 关联 Pattern：PAT-054\n\nset -e\n\n# 颜色输出\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/gateway-memory-fix-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).log\"\n\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $1\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nlog \"🚨 开始 Gateway 内存泄漏紧急修复...\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 1: 检测当前状态\n# ============================================\nlog \"📊 Phase 1: 检测当前状态...\"\n\n# 检查 Gateway 进程\nGATEWAY_PID=$(ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}')\nGATEWAY_MEM=$(ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $6}')\n\nif [ -z \"$GATEWAY_PID\" ]; then\n    log \"${RED}❌ Gateway 进程未运行${NC}\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\nGATEWAY_MB=$((GATEWAY_MEM / 1024))\nlog \"Gateway PID: $GATEWAY_PID\"\nlog \"Gateway 内存: ${GATEWAY_MB} MB\"\n\n# 检查系统可用内存\nAVAILABLE_MEM=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\nlog \"系统可用内存: ${AVAILABLE_MEM} MB\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 2: 判断是否需要重启\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"🔍 Phase 2: 判断是否需要重启...\"\n\nNEED_RESTART=0\nRESTART_REASON=\"\"\n\nif [ $GATEWAY_MB -gt 1800 ]; then\n    NEED_RESTART=1\n    RESTART_REASON=\"Gateway 内存超过 1800 MB (${GATEWAY_MB} MB)\"\n    log \"${RED}🚨 ${RESTART_REASON}${NC}\"\nelif [ $GATEWAY_MB -gt 1500 ]; then\n    NEED_RESTART=1\n    RESTART_REASON=\"Gateway 内存超过 1500 MB (${GATEWAY_MB} MB)\"\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ ${RESTART_REASON}${NC}\"\nelif [ $AVAILABLE_MEM -lt 500 ]; then\n    NEED_RESTART=1\n    RESTART_REASON=\"系统可用内存不足 (${AVAILABLE_MEM} MB)\"\n    log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ ${RESTART_REASON}${NC}\"\nelse\n    log \"${GREEN}✅ Gateway 内存正常 (${GATEWAY_MB} MB)${NC}\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 3: 执行重启（如需要）\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"========================================\"\n\nif [ $NEED_RESTART -eq 1 ]; then\n    log \"🔧 Phase 3: 执行 Gateway 重启...\"\n    log \"原因: $RESTART_REASON\"\n    \n    # 停止 Gateway\n    log \"停止 Gateway...\"\n    systemctl stop openclaw-gateway 2>/dev/null || pkill -f openclaw-gateway || true\n    sleep 5\n    \n    # 检查是否已停止\n    if ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep > /dev/null; then\n        log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ Gateway 未完全停止，强制终止...${NC}\"\n        pkill -9 -f openclaw-gateway || true\n        sleep 2\n    fi\n    \n    # 启动 Gateway\n    log \"启动 Gateway...\"\n    systemctl start openclaw-gateway 2>/dev/null || openclaw gateway start || true\n    sleep 10\n    \n    # 验证重启\n    NEW_PID=$(ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}')\n    NEW_MEM=$(ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $6}')\n    NEW_MB=$((NEW_MEM / 1024))\n    NEW_AVAILABLE=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\n    \n    if [ -n \"$NEW_PID\" ]; then\n        log \"${GREEN}✅ Gateway 重启成功${NC}\"\n        log \"新 PID: $NEW_PID\"\n        log \"新内存: ${NEW_MB} MB (释放 $((GATEWAY_MB - NEW_MB)) MB)\"\n        log \"新可用内存: ${NEW_AVAILABLE} MB (增加 $((NEW_AVAILABLE - AVAILABLE_MEM)) MB)\"\n    else\n        log \"${RED}❌ Gateway 重启失败${NC}\"\n        exit 1\n    fi\nelse\n    log \"${GREEN}✅ 无需重启 Gateway${NC}\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 4: 设置自动监控\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"📊 Phase 4: 设置自动监控...\"\n\n# 创建监控脚本（如果不存在）\nMONITOR_SCRIPT=\"$WORKSPACE/evolver/fixes/gateway-memory-monitor.sh\"\nif [ ! -f \"$MONITOR_SCRIPT\" ]; then\n    cat > \"$MONITOR_SCRIPT\" << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n# Gateway 内存自动监控（每小时执行）\n\nGATEWAY_MEM=$(ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $6}')\nGATEWAY_MB=$((GATEWAY_MEM / 1024))\n\nif [ $GATEWAY_MB -gt 1500 ]; then\n    echo \"[$(date)] Gateway 内存过高: ${GATEWAY_MB} MB\" >> /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/gateway-memory-alerts.log\n    # 可选：自动重启\n    # /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/gateway-memory-leak-fix.sh\nfi\nEOF\n    chmod +x \"$MONITOR_SCRIPT\"\n    log \"✅ 创建监控脚本: $MONITOR_SCRIPT\"\nfi\n\n# 添加到 crontab（如果不存在）\nif ! crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -q \"gateway-memory-monitor.sh\"; then\n    (crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"0 * * * * $MONITOR_SCRIPT\") | crontab -\n    log \"✅ 添加每小时监控到 crontab\"\nfi\n\n# ============================================\n# Phase 5: 生成报告\n# ============================================\nlog \"\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"🎉 Gateway 内存泄漏修复完成\"\nlog \"========================================\"\nlog \"\"\nlog \"修复前状态:\"\nlog \"  Gateway 内存: ${GATEWAY_MB} MB\"\nlog \"  可用内存: ${AVAILABLE_MEM} MB\"\nlog \"\"\n\nif [ $NEED_RESTART -eq 1 ]; then\n    log \"修复后状态:\"\n    log \"  Gateway 内存: ${NEW_MB} MB\"\n    log \"  可用内存: ${NEW_AVAILABLE} MB\"\n    log \"  释放内存: $((GATEWAY_MB - NEW_MB)) MB\"\n    log \"  增加可用: $((NEW_AVAILABLE - AVAILABLE_MEM)) MB\"\n    log \"\"\nfi\n\nlog \"监控设置:\"\nlog \"  监控脚本: $MONITOR_SCRIPT\"\nlog \"  监控频率: 每小时\"\nlog \"  告警阈值: 1500 MB\"\nlog \"\"\nlog \"日志文件: $LOG_FILE\"\nlog \"\"\n\n# 返回状态\nif [ $NEED_RESTART -eq 1 ]; then\n    if [ $NEW_MB -lt 1000 ]; then\n        log \"${GREEN}✅ Gateway 内存已恢复正常${NC}\"\n        exit 0\n    else\n        log \"${YELLOW}⚠️ Gateway 重启后内存仍然较高${NC}\"\n        exit 1\n    fi\nelse\n    log \"${GREEN}✅ Gateway 状态正常${NC}\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/gateway-memory-leak-fix.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7b4c23f61e3a4884aafe412b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/gateway-memory-leak-fix.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7046ba4b2f18449ea15dea9d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/gateway-memory-leak-fix.sh 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3733,"output":1986,"cacheRead":104128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109847,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772368224613}}
